# Portico — environment configuration
#
# ── Gateway ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Point the Claude Agent SDK at your Portkey gateway. Both vars are passed
# straight through to the underlying Anthropic SDK.
#
# Portkey example:
ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.portkey.ai/v1
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-portkey-virtual-key-here
#
# Direct Anthropic (no Portkey):
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Model ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Pin the model. Defaults to claude-sonnet-4-6 if unset.
# PORTICO_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
# PORTICO_MODEL=claude-opus-4-7        # heavier reasoning, slower, pricier
# PORTICO_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5       # cheapest / fastest

# ── System prompt ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Override the built-in Portico identity. Leave unset to use the default,
# which extends the Claude Code agent preset with a short Portico line.
# PORTICO_SYSTEM_PROMPT=You are an internal assistant for Acme Corp. ...
